Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特司令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源于你无能至极的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八魔人名声扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为机师确实出色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为指挥官又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许再发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样作为是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉 是我的指挥不利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥官是我 责任在我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次让他们满意就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据报歌姬号有行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正单舰驶往索伦城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦城？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 可能会有麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索伦城公安局发来的入港航道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认接收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 开始入港程序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入港后 全力配合卫星方面的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全心全意 别让对方产生不必要的戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船的舰长是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我军捕获了部分维甘军机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据彻底细致的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在机体使用的零部件中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了地球圈索伦科技集团独有的素材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球圈的企业在为维甘做事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以派遣本舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往索伦科技所在的卫星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防打草惊蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派遣少数亲信部队前往调查最为合适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我也会随行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令官来歌姬号上…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必要时不惜采取强制手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癌细胞须切除干净
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 很可能伤及平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你一定会反对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这正是我随行的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对维甘不能心慈手软
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会利用你的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走你最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 你对维甘的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那么强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然连战舰都开来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慌啥 你们又不是第一天干这行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这次对手是军队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠钱和威胁很难奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是来调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明还没有切实证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理直气壮一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么按预定计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去会见索伦社负责人 争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一舰之长真不好当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最擅长交涉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游刃有余？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还不至于 很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一出什么意外有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只管专心完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米·卢斯上士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明日野司令的AGE-1吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么近距离目睹传说中的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打扫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 弹射器有点脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有自动清洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 家里的玄关要亲手清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄关？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号如果是家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是玄关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人感觉就像自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和乘员在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 就好像和家人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我算是蕾米的哥哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号所有人里 中尉是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以无话不说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对长官这样说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 每次都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 想看看你有没有空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命可不是自由活动时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回待命室去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道！马上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们协助调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们也希望早日洗清嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免造成不必要的业务损失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次您是一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为调查 其实内容很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只问几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实不擅长干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一片是摆设吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到找到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们不会轻易收手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是维甘占领地球的重要据点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我们计划中不可缺少的一环
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现的太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 蜜蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到沃尔夫少校信号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现证据！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎·穆莱中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在菲利特·明日野中将的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长外出时 本舰指挥由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行使联邦军权限
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取设施控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命中的机动战士队 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出动机动战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然发现与维甘私下勾结的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样的居民区进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会造成很多无辜伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出动机动战士不是唯一的解决办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人征求你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如不歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤亡会进一步扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该考虑把牺牲控制在最小限度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是身为指挥官的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间的迟疑 可能导致无法挽回的恶果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲市民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会服从这样的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士队的指挥由奥布莱特中尉负责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿黛尔使用泰特斯装备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆那家伙 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎 走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被逼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘威胁我们 迫不得已…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保全索伦城 只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蕾丝 上车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我必须去安排工人避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我去完成自己最后的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子压根儿没打算乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经打到这种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这种情形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸还会说那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打败维甘 这是不得已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你说得都对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家谁不难过？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令一定也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信 杰哈特和你战斗时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不再有迷茫 干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不难过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙终究是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莉莎她们情况不妙 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如不歼灭敌人 伤亡会进一步扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间的迟疑 可能带来无法挽回的恶果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把坐标发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用自动驾驶放出AGE-2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想伤害你 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 只为保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是决不能拱手让出这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会耍大牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁死不肯交出情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 善后已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认维甘男子死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 物证全部销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在小黑屋里关一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有东西想给他看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出去感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是无法执行那种命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这么当兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为男人也不光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你还是坐上了高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后只能在战斗中寻求答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空停下脚步烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该超越的既不是老爸也不是别的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 菲利特
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------EDCN2----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:44.14,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}依偎墙头 彻夜 思索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:50.45,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}是否是自己选择的方向 渐渐迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:54.81,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}但是 答案不会乖乖出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.35,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}哪里都不是理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:01.79,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}抬起低垂的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:04.88,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}澄净的朝阳在外守候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.87,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}为觅得自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:12.37,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}须捍卫的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:19.56,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}无法轻易得出的答案 折磨煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:24.93,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}别为一次挫折耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:29.49,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}迈出脚步 试着爱自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:33.60,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}为觅得自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:37.17,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}寻找某种未知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:44.30,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}伤痛 彷徨 痛苦而煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:49.64,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}但是答应我 仅此一次 不要苛责自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:56.11,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}朝前走 鼓起勇气 我的世界
