Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与战友的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此的思念和相互吸引的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次将他们带往激烈的战争漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人的命运 成就历史
